{"title":"Spotted: All-New Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes at Sea Otter","link":"https://bikerumor.com/mavic-cosmic-ultimate-iv-road-shoes/","date":1744407331000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes--1536x1152.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes\" /></p>\n<p>The Mavic booth at Sea Otter Classic is filled to the brim with eye-catching gear and many (<em>many!</em>) custom bikes (<em>more on those later</em>). But once you get over the initial shock of all that eye-catching carbon and titanium, you could spy some unreleased, yet-to-be-ever-seen gear. One new product that really caught my eye were the new Boa-dial Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV road shoes. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV road bike shoes </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes side back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side-back--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This next-gen Cosmic Ultimate IV jumps from the III with all-new reinforced, woven upper construction and updated BOA Li2 dials. Mavic explained that the construction is a Matryx mix of Kevlar and Polyamid yarn, which Mavic claims provides the lowest-possible fiber elongation for the best power transfer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>New Super Stiff Carbon Sole</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes cleat jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-cleat-jpeg-2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new, very ventilated sole is made of Mavic (<em>also?</em>) Matryx carbon. Its “integrated lining weaving” construction and a 100/100 Mavic stiffness rating makes the new Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV the French company’s stiffest road shoe to date.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, that Matryx carbon weave offers a super slick and eye-catching appearance.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Vents for Hotness </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes venting\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-venting--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These aren’t <em>“speed holes,”</em> but cooler heads and feet usually prevail. Mavic’s Matryx upper weaves in jacquard-venting – the variegated weaving pattern leaves openings between alternating fibers to allow for extra airflow without compromising the material’s structural performance. Mavic says this enables them to locate strategically-positioned openings to optimize cooling, and also reduces the need for adhesives, further enhancing ventilation.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Key Features – Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-white--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-white--1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes white\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-white--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-white--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-white--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-white--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-white--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side--1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-side--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-toe--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-toe--1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes toe\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-toe--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-toe--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-toe--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-toe--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-toe--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Material:</strong> Matryx woven upper with integrated venting</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fasteners:</strong> 2x BOA Li2 Fit System dials with woven wires &amp; webbing lace guides</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sole: </strong>Full carbon fiber outsole (rigidity index: 100/100)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tread:</strong> Heel rubber pads</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Cleat compatibility:</strong> 3 bolts (Look, SPD-SL)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight:</strong> 246g actual per shoe</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Availability:</strong> Now </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price:</strong> $500</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes weight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Mavic-Cosmic-Ultimate-IV-Road-Shoes-weight--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mavic.com/en-us/p/cosmic-ultimate-iv-cr2401?variant=7896\">Mavic.com</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mavic-cosmic-ultimate-iv-road-shoes/\">Spotted: All-New Mavic Cosmic Ultimate IV Road Shoes at Sea Otter</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"dda5327999995900c781fd6c141b2b19d7d36bd2b18090e908e6d3778220fb2e","category":"Cycling"}